<title>
Tabla de utilidades de la herramienta de escaneado
</title>
<ptxt>
La herramienta de escaneado SUZUKI dispone de una función de cambio de configuración del módulo de control de arranque sin llave; dicha función opera del modo que se describe a continuación. Para obtener más información, consulte el &#34;Manual del usuario de la herramienta de escaneado SUZUKI&#34;.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
*1: Aplicable al modelo con alarma de seguridad.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "3" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "1.918in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.540in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "3.761in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Elemento
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Ajuste
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Descripción
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Sistema de arranque sin llave
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
ON/  OFF
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Se modifica la configuración de las antenas interiores y exteriores (se permite o no la transmisión de ondas de radio).
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Respuesta (indicador acústico exterior)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
ON/  OFF
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Se modifica la configuración del indicador acústico de advertencia exterior durante la respuesta.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
ON: Activo
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
OFF: Pasiva
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Aviso del área del mando a distancia
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
ON/  OFF
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Se modifica la configuración del indicador acústico de advertencia (ubicado en el juego de instrumentos) durante la alarma de mando a distancia fuera del área de detección.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
ON: Activo
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
OFF: Pasiva
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Aviso de la pila del mando a distancia
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
ON/  OFF
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Se modifica la configuración del aviso de pila del mando a distancia agotada.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
ON: Activo
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
OFF: Pasiva
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Alarma de seguridad (*1)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
ON/  OFF
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
La configuración de la alarma de seguridad ha cambiado.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
ON: Activo
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
OFF: Pasiva
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
